
1.Make sure Node.js is installed.
node -v
npm -v
2. Create Your Project Folder
mkdir number-utils
cd number-utils
3.Initialize NPM and Install Dependencies
npm init -y
npm install express body-parser
This will create:
package.json
node_modules folder

4.Create index.js with the Code
5.Run the Server
node index.js

6.Test the APIs with Tools like:
 Postman (recommended)
Curl (CLI)
Your browser (for GET endpoints)
